                <h2>Lower your total cost of ownership &#x28;TCO&#x29;</h2>
                
                
        
        <h4>Meet your financial objectives</h4>
        <p>Our deduplication and compression capabilities reduce the amount of storage hardware you need.</p>

<p>Thin reclamation allows you to reclaim (and reuse) thin-provisioned LUNs that are no longer required because the data they stored have been deleted.</p>

<p>Storage virtualization support frees you to choose the storage hardware vendor that’s cost effective for you.</p>



        


