        <h4>Introducing the InfoScale family of solutions</h4>
        <p>Certain products from the Storage Foundation High Availability (SFHA) family have transitioned to the newer InfoScale family, the next generation of business continuity and storage management from Veritas.</p>

<p>InfoScale also offers the option of subscription licensing. Overall, the newer products have broader functionality than individual products in the previous SFHA product line. </p>

<ul>
<li>InfoScale solutions include:</li>
<li>InfoScale Enterprise</li>
<li>InfoScale Availability</li>
<li>InfoScale Storage</li>
<li>InfoScale Foundation</li>
<li>InfoScale Operations Manager</li>
</ul>



        
        	
            
