                <h2>InfoScale Foundation</h2>
                
                
        
        <h4>Simplify storage management</h4>
        <p>Designed for heterogeneous online storage management environments, InfoScale Foundation combines industry-leading File System and Volume Manager technology to deliver a comprehensive solution that increases storage utilization and enhances storage I/O path availability.</p>

<p>Key features include:</p>

<ul>
<li>Veritas Volume Manager and File System</li>
<li>Dynamic multi-pathing</li>
<li>Enclosure based naming</li>
<li>Device names using array volume IDs</li>
</ul>



        
        	
            
            	<p class="center-cta">
            
                
                	
	                
	                
