						<div class="content-col">

    
    
    
    


        
            
                <h2>InfoScale Enterprise</h2>
                
                
        
        <h4>World-class availability meets world-class storage management.</h4>
        <p>Drawing on our long heritage of world-class availability and storage management solutions, InfoScale Enterprise helps your IT teams realize more reliable operations and highly protected information and applications across your physical and virtual infrastructures. </p>

<p>With enterprise class resiliency and software-defined storage features for critical services across your datacenter infrastructure, InfoScale Enterprise helps ensure that your IT operations run at their highest performance levels. The solution provides high availability and disaster recovery for complex multi-tiered applications across any distance.</p>

<p>In addition to InfoScale Storage and InfoScale Availability features, InfoScale Enterprise includes:</p>

<ul>
<li>Support for Oracle RAC</li>
<li>Support for Sybase ASE CE</li>
<li>High availability support for Cluster File System </li>
</ul>



        
        	
            
            	<p class="center-cta">
            
                
                	
	                
	                
                        <a class="cta" href="/product/software-defined-storage/infoscale-enterprise">
					
                
                
                
                More about InfoScale Enterprise </a>
            </p>
        


</div>
